					<![CDATA[
						 <p>Bingo! As I am generally wont, my aim was to 'canonize' as much of the extant CotBG material as possible. I wasn't sure I had a place for 1564 until it occurred to me that they clearly weren't <em>components</em> of the thing, but <em>messengers</em> for it.</p> <p>That's a good skip, btw. You should be proud.</p> 
				 	]]>
